Description:
A Place To Call Home
A not-to-be-missed opportunity to secure your future, within walking distance to Brimbank Shopping Centre, Albanvale Primary School, public transport and parklands, this well-maintained BV family home boasts an abundance of space and light. Offering great living accommodation internal & external - ideal for first home buyers or investors who will relish the opportunity. Comprising of 3 spacious bedrooms with BIRs, spacious L shaped lounge and well-appointed kitchen with ample cupboard space and central bathroom. Other features include reverse cycle A/C, hardwood floor boards throughout, gas cooking appliances, double lock-up garage and a massive backyard for your children to enjoy. Makes this one of the most highly sought after family homes available. Call now to arrange the inspection.

Description:
Grand Family Home In Premier Locale
Superbly located within walking distance to Ginifer train station, Holy Eucharist Parish, Holy Eucharist Primary school and close proximity to the expanding Sunshine hospital and Victoria university, this family home ticks all the boxes. Comprising 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 with mirror BIR's, great sized front verandah, the kitchen adjoins the meals area and a great sized family room. Features polished floorboards, ducted heating, space heater, air conditioner, alarm system and rear alfresco. Ample off street parking plus an oversized lock up garage with 3 phase power and workshop. An inspection is highly recommended.

Description:
First Class Location, First Class Renovations.
Tastefully renovated and perfectly located in a pocket of Taylors Lakes, offering an expansive floorplan with top end finishes, you'll fall in love at first step. Greeted with a spacious living and library area flowing into an open plan gourmet kitchen with stone benchtops, top end stainless steel appliances and soft closing drawers overlooking a huge, open plan meals and family area brimming with natural light. Step outside to a beautiful undercover entertainment area, with built in BBQ and offering lovely garden views. Living quarters offer three spacious bedrooms, master with built in robe and stunning ensuite, remaining with built in robes, study/optional 4th bedroom and stylish central bathroom. Other features include: Ducted heating, evaporative cooling, solar panels, water tanks, huge garden shed with power, security shutters and double carport. Moments away from Watergardens Town Centre, local schools, parks and public transport, this is a location the whole family can benefit from. Contact Andrew or Justin to inspect today!!

Under Offer
***This property is available for inspection by appointment-Please contact us to arrange a suitable time****
On its own separately-titled block this freestanding villa is sure to impress with its light, space and location making it an ideal first home, easy investment or terrific downsize opportunity. Absolutely immaculate from start to finish, the home's light-filled interior offers quality accommodation comprising three genuinely large bedrooms with BIRs, central bathroom and separate WC, spacious open plan lounge through to the dining area and adjoining kitchen. Add to this ducted heating and evaporative cooling, full-size laundry, plus a private courtyard, under house storage, oversized garage (remote-controlled) and additional driveway parking. Close proximity to the best of Niddrie including popular schools, public transport options and easy freeway access, parks and trails, as well as Keilor Road cafes, restaurants and vibrant shopping precinct.

Description:
UNDER OFFER
***This property is available for inspection by appointment. Please contact us to arrange a suitable time***
Surrounded by established gardens on a substantial high-side block (approx 547sqm), this architectural showpiece is sure to exceed all expectations with its vast three-level floorplan, quality features throughout and esteemed Valley Lake location. Meticulously detailed, the home's beautifully appointed interior showcases five large bedrooms (two with WIRs and private ensuites), stylish main bathroom with spa bath and guest powder room (fourth WC). Spacious and versatile living zones include a separate lounge/theatre room, expansive open-design family/dining areas with valley views accompanied by a premium kitchen with quality appliances and ample cupboard space. Impressive highlights include heating and cooling throughout, alarm and video intercom, square set ceilings, new carpets and solid hardwood floors, family-sized laundry and large storeroom/cellar. Step outside to discover an al-fresco style entertaining deck and wonderfully wide north-facing backyard with expansive lawn areas and additional decking, plus the added appeal of a remote-control double garage with internal entry. Close to a range of lifestyle attractions including Steele Creek trails and acres of parkland, public transport options and freeway access, as well as the area's primary and secondary schools, Keilor Road's renowned cafes, restaurants and retail precinct.
Actual address 26A The Avenue, Niddrie.
*** COVID-19 Announcement ***
If you're attending a Private Appointment, we request that you only attend if you are fit and healthy to do so and not under any self-isolation conditions. We request that you maintain a healthy distance from our team members, and if requested wait outside until the property is ready for the appointment. Lastly, please refrain from touching items/fixtures and doors within the properties. If you would like to view something in particular, please request the agent's assistance. Thank you.

Description:
PERFECT LOCATION THE PAVILIONS ESTATE
Situated in a highly sought-after location within 10mins drive to Major Shopping Centres (Keilor Road, Niddrie, Millera Mall, Centre Way & Dinah Parade). 10 mins walk to Bus and schools.
Ideal Low Maintenance home buyer or investor.
This Proudly Maintained Home offers:
3 Bedrooms (BIR), master with ensuite & walk in Robe
Separate Loungeroom with good natural light
Kitchen with dining and step out to garden area
Tiled bathroom & separate laundry
Lock up garage and security alarm
Ducted heating, evaporative cooling, gas cook top, wall oven and more
Low maintenance
For inspection phone Joe Albioli 0438 133 123
SEALED BID Friday 17th of April @ 5:00pm
COVID-19 UPDATE
We are still conducting business during this time but with the safety & health of others and the team as the highest priority.
We will be conducting private inspections only with stricter guidelines so please contact our office to arrange a viewing.
During our Private Inspections we will ask that only one person is allowed into the property at any time. We ask that no surfaces are touched. We will have the property ready for you to inspect prior to your arrival.
We ask anyone that has recently returned from overseas and if you are unwell to ensure you do not attend any inspections. Contact our office to organise alternative viewing arrangements. This also means if you have been next to anyone that may have been overseas or unwell.
We thank everyone for their co-operation and patience during this time. Stay Safe & Healthy!

Description:
UNDER OFFER
***This property is available for inspection by appointment. Please contact us to arrange a suitable time***
On a wonderfully wide block (approx 736sqm) backing onto reserve, this distinctive home delivers a ready-to-enjoy lifestyle with its terrific entertaining spaces, quality enhancements and self-contained apartment below making it a perfect for growing/extended families. Picture-perfect from start to finish, the home's impressive interior boasts a large master bedroom with its own dressing room and stylish ensuite, together with two additional bedrooms (BIRs) and deluxe main bathroom complete with freestanding bath and frameless shower. Add to this a spacious central living room leading through to the open family/dining area accompanied by a superb stone-bench kitchen with soft-close cabinetry, ample cupboard space, quality cooking appliances and double dishwasher. Other stand-out features include zoned ducted heating and refrigerated cooling, plantation shutters and solid hardwood floors, NBN connection, plus the unique appeal of a separate under-house area with studio-style bedroom/lounge, bathroom and kitchen/meals. Stacker doors reveal an elevated deck with leafy outlook and expansive backyard garden with decked entertaining area and outdoor spa, plus an enormous storage shed and remote-control double garage via paved driveway. Walking distance to McNamara Avenue shops and cafes, primary and secondary schools, parks and trails, it's also close to public transport (buses and trams), easy freeway access along with Essendon Fields, Keilor Road shops and restaurants.
*** COVID-19 Announcement ***
If you're attending a Private Appointment, we request that you only attend if you are fit and healthy to do so and not under any self-isolation conditions. We request that you maintain a healthy distance from our team members, and if requested wait outside until the property is ready for the appointment. Lastly, please refrain from touching items/fixtures and doors within the properties. If you would like to view something in particular, please request the agent's assistance. Thank you.

Description:
Timeless Modern Construction, Family Sized Home, Highly Serviced Location.
A rare opportunity to purchase a home of outstanding modern construction quality in one of the most exclusive streets in St Albans. The profile of Bent street showcases quality built homes in walking vicinity to Ginifer Station, Cairnlea Shopping Town, Western Ring Road, Victoria University and Western Health (Sunshine Hospital).
Ready for immediate enjoyment with a refreshed presentation comprising 3 bedrooms with built in robes, master with en-suite, study, tiled second bathroom, 2 toilets and large laundry. The huge floorplan offers a front formal living area with stunning bay window which can easily double as a 4th bedroom.
Open plan living offers kitchen with island bench top and stainless steel appliances while the family area opens up to a neat outdoor area offering plenty of room for entertaining, hobbies and pets.
Additional features include a lock up remote garage, with rear access to court yard which also has side access to the home, hardwood flooring, ample storage, ducted heating, split system cooling, alarm system, plantation shutters and down lights.
Bigger and better than most - the property offers 18 squares of superior, strategic single level living in an accessible and highly serviced location.

Description:
Prime Location - Huge Potential - Rare Opportunity !!!
Situated in the most prestigious part of St.Albans with excellent access to local amenities, this spacious property offers homebuyers and vigilant investors a rare opportunity with great potential. Redevelopment options (STCA) include retaining/renovating the existing home and building a brand new dwelling on an allotment of approximately 610m2 or demolishing and building a multi unit development site at a fantastic location. You can´t go wrong, but reap the rewards of this smart investment in a highly sought after pocket of the suburb.
Interior consists of two decent size bedrooms, spacious lounge room, central bathroom, kitchen with gas appliances alongside the dining room, opening to a sunroom comprising the laundry. Complemented with ample storage, natural timber floors lies all across.
Beautifully landscaped low maintenance backyard has plenty of room for outdoor living, an undercover verandah, a peaceful gazebo area, a shed for extra storage and an undercover veggie garden.
You have everything you need at a short walking distance such as the Alfrieda Street Shopping Strip (220m approx.), St.Albans Main Road Marketplace and St.Albans Community Centre (450m approx.), St.Albans Train Station (550m approx.), St.Albans Secondary College (950m approx.), St.Albans East Primary School (1km approx.), Victoria University (1.5km approx.) with numerous cafes/restaurants, parks and easy access to the Western Ring Road.
Contact C.Burak Binatli on 0455 663 331 to book in for an inspection today!!!
- Full of potential to develop (STCA) or renovate
- Decent block size of 610sqm approx.
- Fantastic location,within the shopping precinct
- Super convenience, surrounded by amenities
- Walking distance to train station,local transport
- A short stroll to schools,cafes,parks,etc
- Spacious, neat backyard and outdoor living area
- Easy access to Freeway, Western Ring Road
View this magnificent property now!Won´t last long
